  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\nThis Part applies:\n\n  1. (1) to a _small non-directive insurer_ ; and\n  2. (2) in relation to a _small non-directive insurer_ , to any _person_ who is:\n     1. (a) a _Conduct Rules non-executive director_ ;\n     2. (b) approved under section 59 of _FSMA_ by either:\n        1. (i) the _PRA_ ; or\n        2. (ii) the _FCA_ , in relation to a relevant senior management function;\n     3. (c) a _certification employee_ ;\n     4. (d) an _employee_ who should have been approved under section 59 of _FSMA_ by either:\n        1. (i) the _PRA_ ; or\n        2. (ii) the _FCA_ , in relation to a relevant senior management function; or\n     5. (e) an _employee_ who is performing a function that would have been a _controlled function_ but for [Non-Solvency II Firms – Senior Management Functions 2.3](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---senior-management-functions#b324ce6a53024b6db0056695b55eed5d \"Non-Solvency II Firms – Senior Management Functions 2.3\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part the following definition shall apply:\n\n_employee_\n\nhas the meaning given in [Non-solvency II Firms – Certification 1.2](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms-certification#d729dc37c48f4ec1a308dde7c7d1be7b \"Non-solvency II Firms – Certification 1.2\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n1A\n\n###  Scope of Conduct Standards\n\n1A.1\n\nIf you are a natural person who is approved under section 59 of _FSMA_ by either:\n\n  1. (1) the _PRA_ ; or\n  2. (2) the _FCA_ , in relation to a _relevant senior management function_ ,\n\nyou must comply at all times with all of the _conduct standards_.\n\n*Effective: 03/07/2017*\n\n1A.2\n\nIf you are a _Conduct Rules non-executive director_ , you must comply at all times with the _conduct standards_ specified in [2.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e \"2.1\") to [2.3](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4 \"2.3\"), [2.7](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#1801cea6da834acaa42c20f578ae83a5 \"2.7\") and [2.8](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#9aa0b3f13fcf46cf8acc84dabb0d09e6 \"2.8\").\n\n*Effective: 03/07/2017*\n\n1A.3\n\nIf you are an _employee_ of a type specified in [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(c), [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(d) or [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(e) you must comply at all times with the _conduct standards_ specified in [2.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e \"2.1\") to to [2.3](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4 \"2.3\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n1A.4\n\nA _firm_ must require:\n\n  1. (1) a natural _person_ of a type specified in [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(b) to observe all of the _conduct standards_ ; and\n  2. (2) an _employee_ of a type specified in [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(c), [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(d) or [1.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc \"1.1\")(2)(e) to observe the _conduct standards_ specified in [2.1](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e \"2.1\") to [2.3](/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4 \"2.3\").\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n2\n\n###  Conduct Standards\n\n2.1\n\nConduct Standard 1: You must act with integrity.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.2\n\nConduct Standard 2: You must act with due skill, care and diligence.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.3\n\nConduct Standard 3: You must be open and co-operative with the _FCA_ , the _PRA_ and other regulators.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.4\n\nConduct Standard 4: You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the _firm_ for which you are responsible is controlled effectively.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.5\n\nConduct Standard 5: You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the _firm_ for which you are responsible complies with the relevant requirements and standards of the _regulatory system_.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.6\n\nConduct Standard 6: You must take reasonable steps to ensure that any delegation of your responsibilities is to an appropriate _person_ and that you oversee the discharge of the delegated responsibility effectively.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.7\n\nConduct Standard 7: You must disclose appropriately any information of which the _FCA_ or the _PRA_ would reasonably expect to have notice.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*\n\n2.8\n\nConduct Standard 8: When exercising your responsibilities, you must pay due regard to the interests of current and potential future _policyholders_ in ensuring the provision by the _firm_ of an appropriate degree of protection for their insured benefits.\n\n*Effective: 07/03/2016*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"a44b3c4245764beead81fd1896b8037c\" id=\"e2cdb5d9724a4ae29a46f9c98ef3d305\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"6fc7f2002fab4f18830f880975d3a036\" id=\"f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part applies:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67108\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-eb68d2dd8250400d81d6977d3bfaac41\" title=\"small non-directive insurer\">small non-directive insurer</a></em>; and</li>\n<li>(2) in relation to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67108\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-eb68d2dd8250400d81d6977d3bfaac41\" title=\"small non-directive insurer\">small non-directive insurer</a></em>, to any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53235\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bb5dee02540647f88ded5c69be5c567f\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> who is:</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(a) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78125\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fe19114715c34e35bd07e96896ecdb72\" title=\"Conduct Rules non-executive director\">Conduct Rules non-executive director</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(b) approved under section 59 of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em> by either:</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(i) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(ii) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em>, in relation to a <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67050\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-776c0b7f70d94bd7842daf2e1ca39a2c\" title=\"relevant senior management function\">relevant senior management function</a>;</li>\n</ol>\n<li>(c) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52564\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f42fcd52d02845298b099cb7f4c95ed8\" title=\"certification employee\">certification employee</a></em>; </li>\n<li>(d) an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88203\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bd44f5a9ba104a1bbca2cb2054875458\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em> who should have been approved under section 59 of <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em> by either:</li>\n<ol>\n<li>(i) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(ii) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em>, in relation to a<span style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"> </span><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67050\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-776c0b7f70d94bd7842daf2e1ca39a2c\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"relevant senior management function\">relevant senior management function</a><span style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\">;</span> or</li>\n</ol>\n<li>(e) an <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88203\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bd44f5a9ba104a1bbca2cb2054875458\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em> who is performing a function that would have been a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52215\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-77ed05e95e9144549fdcd84ae397fcab\" title=\"controlled function\">controlled function</a></em> but for <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---senior-management-functions#b324ce6a53024b6db0056695b55eed5d\" title=\"Non-Solvency II Firms – Senior Management Functions 2.3\">Non-Solvency II Firms – Senior Management Functions 2.3</a>.</li>\n</ol></ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards/03-07-2017#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"f5ca5464d9e64b6fa92cfbfca6a3bfef\" id=\"492cdcb18e5c42ea93840c33b81fc059\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part the following definition shall apply:</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88203\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bd44f5a9ba104a1bbca2cb2054875458\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">has the meaning given in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms-certification#d729dc37c48f4ec1a308dde7c7d1be7b\" title=\"Non-solvency II Firms – Certification 1.2\">Non-solvency II Firms – Certification 1.2</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"50a2149deeaf49cfb00e36a6430c9f72\" id=\"8e071bd1e7bf4a4e9c7b88bb8dcfac50\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1A\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tScope of Conduct Standards\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"78c89e944b7a445994557d33ce5a8508\" id=\"3135b9021a314226af3ed48537b77e8e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1A.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If you are a natural person who is approved under section 59 of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em> by either:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(2) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67148\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-14dd9b12d1064671881fb4bdb56f03d5\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em>, in relation to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67050\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-776c0b7f70d94bd7842daf2e1ca39a2c\" title=\"relevant senior management function\">relevant senior management function</a></em>,</li>\n</ol>\n<p>you must comply at all times with all of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67033\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a237be2d38ef407da1d7b08d58c086f8\" title=\"conduct standards\">conduct standards</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/07/2017\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"a4ae4afc94494cd0bc569c19311bcb12\" id=\"9937b26cfab34ea8a65dba3636f4c2d3\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1A.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If you are a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"78125\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-fe19114715c34e35bd07e96896ecdb72\" title=\"Conduct Rules non-executive director\">Conduct Rules non-executive director</a></em>, you must comply at all times with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67033\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a237be2d38ef407da1d7b08d58c086f8\" title=\"conduct standards\">conduct standards</a></em> specified in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e\" title=\"2.1\">2.1</a> to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4\" title=\"2.3\">2.3</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#1801cea6da834acaa42c20f578ae83a5\" title=\"2.7\">2.7</a> and <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#9aa0b3f13fcf46cf8acc84dabb0d09e6\" title=\"2.8\">2.8</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/07/2017\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"ff94e51b847a4d728cf2412472f16491\" id=\"fc48c8ca37b74bff88dbc5231aabb741\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1A.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>If you are an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88203\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bd44f5a9ba104a1bbca2cb2054875458\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em> of a type specified in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(c), <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(d) or <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(e) you must comply at all times with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67033\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a237be2d38ef407da1d7b08d58c086f8\" title=\"conduct standards\">conduct standards</a></em> specified in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e\" title=\"2.1\">2.1</a> to to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4\" title=\"2.3\">2.3</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"2900d1e221f74b0896d31d431d29d5aa\" id=\"fa9c6f737fb94b3ebb7c05691c56935a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1A.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must require:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a natural <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67149\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-654681c4344848d382fd428d0fcd0838\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> of a type specified in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(b) to observe all of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67033\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a237be2d38ef407da1d7b08d58c086f8\" title=\"conduct standards\">conduct standards</a></em>; and</li>\n<li>(2) an <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"88203\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bd44f5a9ba104a1bbca2cb2054875458\" title=\"employee\">employee</a></em> of a type specified in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(c), <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(d) or <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#f4dbc1b2e8e4437e9475d6e7b06425cc\" style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\" title=\"1.1\">1.1</a>(2)(e) to observe the <em style=\"text-indent: -14.3px;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"67033\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a237be2d38ef407da1d7b08d58c086f8\" title=\"conduct standards\">conduct standards</a></em> specified in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e\" title=\"2.1\">2.1</a> to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-solvency-ii-firms---conduct-standards#2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4\" title=\"2.3\">2.3</a>. </li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"21680d1432e244a4bdc8d7b57beec958\" id=\"b6ef98f9d8bd4ca6a413f68777944aa5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tConduct Standards\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"c9e9bb8d9b4c4d449d37725d8f487e09\" id=\"ff997b9e4b104ef8a64809e7115e786e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 1:</span> You must act with integrity.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"97b95ac316f04ecf8e0f06da8f751215\" id=\"f402a58e34cf49758e97f7076f5009c1\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 2: </span>You must act with due skill, care and diligence.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"f7ce535625374f96a0a1328efe9dc7de\" id=\"2de16f8f97d1497f9cf5b0cff876eae4\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 3:</span> You must be open and co-operative with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> and other regulators.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"b80ec6fe06a64a5388b0f4e6ef6001a7\" id=\"7b1f656608244ffc99d646cf94c4befb\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 4:</span> You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> for which you are responsible is controlled effectively.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"7d31e73b5908499a9761dabd27b8cabf\" id=\"72bde6435555414793d28609a6b66d52\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.5\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 5:</span> You must take reasonable steps to ensure that the business of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> for which you are responsible complies with the relevant requirements and standards of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52098\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-8b88ef3d27fa45aeba6c11a8df1a92ac\" title=\"regulatory system\">regulatory system</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"1268f510b82d42d198509204919fc0cd\" id=\"95121b0b04e94dfbbcb60bce0f3254ec\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.6\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 6:</span> You must take reasonable steps to ensure that any delegation of your responsibilities is to an appropriate <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53235\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-bb5dee02540647f88ded5c69be5c567f\" title=\"person\">person</a></em> and that you oversee the discharge of the delegated responsibility effectively.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"67eeb14877db40ad84989436ceedb004\" id=\"1801cea6da834acaa42c20f578ae83a5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.7\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 7:</span> You must disclose appropriately any information of which the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52718\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a6adfc5faca24b3186f3f7bee3c6db22\" title=\"FCA\">FCA</a></em> or the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> would reasonably expect to have notice.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"feb777e8b0e84c21af2eaef583fc455d\" id=\"9aa0b3f13fcf46cf8acc84dabb0d09e6\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.8\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><span class=\"rule-style-1\">Conduct Standard 8:</span> When exercising your responsibilities, you must pay due regard to the interests of current and potential future <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53224\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e156c275391d4461b0834559bee81894\" title=\"policyholders\">policyholders</a></em> in ensuring the provision by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> of an appropriate degree of protection for their insured benefits.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t07/03/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
